cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is about searching and ranking pre-trained neural network models for common tasks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper specifically focuses on a novel algorithm for ranking models based on their suitability relative to a target dataset, which is a problem that is relevant to all of these sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.IR, in that order.
